===Noun===
'''martin''' (''plural'' '''martins''')

# Any of various [[passerine]] [[bird]]s of the family ''[[Hirundinidae]]'', which also includes [[swallow]]s, that catch [[insect]]s whilst flying.

  2. a bird that was discovered in uganda in 1846 and is now refered to the emo bird because of its long hair used to protect its eyes from sand. it appeared in an issue of the beano comic recently, that called it eric the emo.

